description.narrative: (Democratic Republic of the Congo): FY2016 funds will be used to provide coordination, monitoring, evaluation, analytic, and research services for the Mission's Country Development Cooperation Strategy and a Joint Education Program between USAID/DRC and UK Department of International Development (DFID). This mechanism will enable the mission to monitor and evaluate its programs in an integrated fashion that will address interconnected development challenges and maximize synergies across sectors as well as across development agencies. .
